---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const updated = 'June 24, 2026';
---
<Layout
  current=""
  title="Cookie Policy | RRS Realty Group"
  description="How RRSRealtyGroup.com uses cookies and similar technologies, and how you can control them."
>
  <section class="page-head">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p>How we use cookies and similar technologies — and how you can control them.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top:40px">
    <div class="prose">
      <p class="post-meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <p>This Cookie Policy explains how RRS Realty Group ("we," "us," or "our") uses cookies and similar technologies on RRSRealtyGroup.com (the "Site"). It should be read together with our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

      <h2>What Cookies Are</h2>
      <p>Cookies are small text files that a website stores on your device to make the site work, remember your preferences, or understand how the site is used. Similar technologies include local storage and pixels. Cookies can be "session" (deleted when you close your browser) or "persistent" (kept until they expire or you delete them).</p>

      <h2>How We Use Cookies</h2>
      <p>We aim to keep our use of cookies minimal. We may use:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Strictly necessary</strong> — small amounts of browser storage needed for the Site to function and to remember choices such as whether you've dismissed our cookie notice.</li>
        <li><strong>Functionality</strong> — to remember basic preferences so the Site works smoothly.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics (if enabled)</strong> — to understand, in aggregate, how visitors use the Site so we can improve it. We do not use this information to identify you personally.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do <strong>not</strong> use cookies to sell your personal information or to serve you targeted third‑party advertising.</p>

      <h2>Third‑Party Cookies</h2>
      <p>Some features rely on third parties that may set their own cookies or receive your request data, including our web font provider and the provider that processes our contact form. These third parties handle data under their own policies. We encourage you to review their privacy and cookie notices.</p>

      <h2>Managing Cookies</h2>
      <p>Most browsers let you block or delete cookies through their settings. You can also usually set your browser to warn you before accepting cookies. Note that blocking some cookies may affect how the Site works. To learn how to manage cookies in your browser, check its help documentation. Some browsers also offer a "Do Not Track" or Global Privacy Control signal, which we honor where required by law.</p>

      <h2>Your Consent</h2>
      <p>By continuing to use the Site after being shown our cookie notice, you consent to our use of cookies as described in this policy. You can withdraw consent at any time by adjusting your browser settings.</p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. Changes are effective when posted on this page with a revised date.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about our use of cookies? Email us at <a href="mailto:rrsrealtygroup@gmail.com">rrsrealtygroup@gmail.com</a>.</p>

      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2em"><em>This template is provided for convenience and is not legal advice. Have an attorney review it for your specific situation before relying on it.</em></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
